mqvpn (0.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix server crash (SIGSEGV) when a non-H3 QUIC probe connects without
    a matching ALPN — cb_write_socket and cb_path_removed blindly cast
    mqvpn_server_t * to svr_conn_t * before H3 setup (issue #4282).
  * Fix client busy-loop on -XQC_EMP_CREATE_PATH: close path permanently
    instead of scheduling retries that can never succeed (OOM / cap hit).
  * Fix netlink try_readd busy-loop during WiFi reassociation bursts.
  * client: abort QUIC handshake after 5 s stall and rotate primary path.
  * client: rotate primary path on reconnect to escape stale connections.
  * Control API: unify listen address as "addr:port" via control_listen in
    INI ([Control] Listen) and JSON (control_listen); legacy Port/Addr keys
    remain supported for backward compatibility.
  * Add fixed (pinned) per-user IP address support (server-side).
  * Add congestion control setting in INI config file.
  * Add unit test for server crash regression (non-H3 probe).
  * Windows client support.

 -- mqvpn maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Thu, 07 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mqvpn (0.3.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add experimental backup_fec multipath scheduler (FEC repair on standby path).
  * Bump xquic to 4b93fb1 (fix FEC memory leak in repair symbol cleanup).
  * Refactor scheduler dispatch into mqvpn_apply_scheduler() shared helper.
  * Add test_scheduler unit test for scheduler dispatch.

 -- mqvpn maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Sat, 26 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mqvpn (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add FEC (Forward Error Correction) and packet reinjection support.
  * Add support for all xquic schedulers and congestion control settings.
  * Add cipher suite configuration options.
  * Add user authentication support (username in addition to pre-shared key).
  * Add path rotation on startup.
  * Add ICMP handling support.
  * Backup mode: use xquic standby API for schedulers that support it.
  * Add routes management options (--gateway, --no-gateway).
  * Refactor tick() and client_new() into focused helper functions.
  * Fix memory leaks in client teardown path.
  * Fix multipath route detection errors.
  * Merge main: CMakeLists.txt now includes icmp.c.

 -- mqvpn maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mqvpn (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Add backup/failover path support (--backup-path).
  * Add TCP control API for runtime user and path management.

